\pandocbounded{\includegraphics[keepaspectratio]{figures/ntop_bo_50_300/fig-nmf-k5-heatmap-1.png}}
\caption{Gene program overlap heatmap for standard NMF at elbow-selected
rank \(k = 5\). Each cell shows the number of top genes from a given
factor (rows) overlapping established PDAC gene programs (columns). The
three core programs from \(k = 3\) are recovered; two additional factors
overlap Exocrine-like and iCAF signatures, capturing transcriptional
variance not aligned with survival outcomes.
